Amy, Kiki and Carla are three of the hardest working, yet some of the most underappreciated moms. Amy reaches her breaking point at a PTA meeting when the chairlady, the overzealous Gwendolyn, asks the mums to bake no-gluten, no-sugar, no-salt, no-fat, no-nuts cookies. The trio decide to embark on a path to change the norm of being a mom. The film s super-talented cast try their hardest to elevate the feeble storyline and above-water jokes. The multitalented cast ensemble includes: Mila Kunis, Kristen Bell, Kathryn Hahn, Christina Applegate and Jada Pinkett-Smith.